{"tid":2331560,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"著書談六四涉尋釁滋事  《紐時》前攝記因言被捕","createTime":"2020-12-19T01:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T03:24:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a60f545ecd1b37b67483b146c8aa76133323adea","tid":2331560,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T01:44:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201219/O6G4DGN4QRF63CX4Y6O55HGHUA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201219%2FO6G4DGN4QRF63CX4Y6O55HGHUA%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=9f458fad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201219%2FO6G4DGN4QRF63CX4Y6O55HGHUA%2F&h=12a95768\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201219/O6G4DGN4QRF63CX4Y6O55HGHUA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n著書談六四涉尋釁滋事 <br />\n《紐時》前攝記因言被捕<br />\n<br />\n曾任《紐約時報》北京分社攝影記者、現為中國公民記者的杜斌周三（16日）被警方帶走拘留，他被指涉「尋釁滋事」，可能與他近年在網上發言及所著書本，講及六四和長春圍城等歷史的書籍有關，他近日也將有一本主題為共產主義的新書推出。杜的朋友胡佳對本報表示，當局近日已多次傳喚杜斌，要求他刪除Twitter的內容，並打聽他是不是還在寫書。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：拘留屆滿前改監視居住  警搜維權者家撿《蘋果》<br />\n<br />\n杜斌被帶走拘留的消息於昨凌晨傳出，指他於周三早上9時左右失去聯絡，他的妹妹翌日收到警方電話告知，指杜斌涉「尋釁滋事」被關押在大興區拘留所。據知，杜斌的妹妹問警察：「哥哥整天在家裏待着，怎麼會尋釁滋事呢？」對方沒有透露具體情況，只說杜斌經常在網上發表一些敏感的東西，讓家人勸勸他。<br />\n<br />\n杜斌的朋友胡佳對本報表示，杜斌與他和其他維權人士不同，杜斌不是活動行動者或是組織者，杜斌是一個公民記者，也想不到杜斌在被傳喚多次後，還會遭帶走拘留。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ohmgx3uannx_1q1y5aZ8jBRIwN0=/1758x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K3BQUJWFDNHSVFYWKSFQWHCOIY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOhmgx3uannx_1q1y5aZ8jBRIwN0%3D%2F1758x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK3BQUJWFDNHSVFYWKSFQWHCOIY.jpg&h=b6f8eace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■杜斌著作《馬三家咆哮》，揭露勞教所濫施酷刑。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下月推新書談共產主義<br />\n<br />\n據了解，杜斌近年專注在。。。。。。。。。。。。胡佳指，現在比起2013年、他與杜斌家人一起呼籲外界營救杜斌時已經不一樣，中國現在政治氣氛複雜得多。<br />\n<br />\n杜斌下月亦有新書《赤色恐怖：列寧的共產主義實驗》面世，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n今年以來，中國不斷拘捕記者，包括前往武漢報道肺炎疫情而遭逮捕的張展、陳秋實等，本月又以危害國家安全為由，拘留一名彭博新聞社的中國員工范若伊。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者/《紐約時報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WcsWm1La-FsCXAzNvWBV7pxjZTU=/394x591/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XTYYZBKND5EHJK7IGBU24X2T6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWcsWm1La-FsCXAzNvWBV7pxjZTU%3D%2F394x591%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXTYYZBKND5EHJK7IGBU24X2T6U.jpg&h=557d6db5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"879eac28680c46b645672fd6915f41cea4443a1d","tid":2331560,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T01:49:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1dfa8df0aebf92d90596ee5a552085556faa93e4","tid":2331560,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:20:24.000Z","msg":"中共談虎色變😓"},{"pid":"1ccec2ae31b220dbc5cc3e589334abc2f44640b3","tid":2331560,"uid":373532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:24:39.000Z","msg":"嘩屌 依條友啲書好出名㗎喎"}]}